{"title":"何年何月归故乡","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":5,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"何年何月归故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自台湾某君来信）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在异乡心在家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归程万里苦无法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身不由己笼中鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心急如焚乱如麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思悠悠，恨悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生苦恼几时休？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路迢迢，海茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何年何月归故乡？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼吾父莫心急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他日有机聚首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到那时大人高兴儿欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家团聚乐无忧。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}